TopicTitle: Unknown Industries KV-2 MUP Hawking (we apologize for the drunken engineers)

Articles.Content:
Well, it\'s not out fault. We couldn\'t stop them. Once the engineers found Jeb\'s secret stash of vodka they sat down and furiously scribbled on a napkin, incepting this monster

KV-2 Mostly Useless Plane Hawking

The drawings were put to use to impress the senators, but being kerbals they ordered us to mass produce it.

The only problem is that there\'s no purpose to it, and we\'ve had to rebuild the VAB fourteen times because of explosions.

When we rolled it out to the launchpad, we knew it wasn\'t going to look good to our insurers.

About 20 second after liftoff the entire back of the wing flew away to save orphans, and left us with no control

This was the last image we recived. Contact from KSC and the nearby cities were lost about .25 seconds after this image.

The good news is there is no trace of the insurance office, or any civilization, so no lawsuits

Whoops.

Knock yourself out

Try splitting those large wings into two seperate ones on each side, then add the elevators just as you did on the bottom.

But for now it is basically just a huge target saying 'Shoot me!' all over it!

Hope this helped!
